title: When Nothing Is All You've Got
description: PURCHASE LINKS BELOW, Available in KU“Move like the wind, protect your face, keep your eyes on the target, and don’t get dead.”I am the daughter of a King,but I am no princess.I am loathed by many,but feared by more.To one I was nothing,to another I am everything.I am a pawn in their game,a fighter in their ring.My name is Nada,and this is life in the underworld.
author: Kirsty Dallas
